node.title: Homicide probe underway after woman killed in Christchurch
node.content: ["A homicide investigation is under way in Christchurch after a woman was killed overnight.", "Police were called to reports of an assault in Hawke Street, New Brighton at 10.40pm last night.\u00a0", "The victim, a woman in her 40s, was unresponsive when emergency services arrived, and tragically died while being transported to hospital.", "A 43-year-old man was taken into custody at the scene and is assisting Police with our enquiries.", "At this stage no charges have been laid.\u00a0", "A scene examination will continue today in the vicinity of the Countdown carpark in Hawke Street."]
